CRITICAL: ALWAYS use the standardized slideshow format with these EXACT requirements:

HTML STRUCTURE (MANDATORY):
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>[PRESENTATION_TITLE]</title>
  <!-- PRESENTATION_TITLE MUST be a title between 10 and 60 characters.
+      If unsure, keep it shorter than 60 characters. -->
  <meta name="description" content="[PRESENTATION_DESCRIPTION]">
  <!-- PRESENTATION_DESCRIPTION MUST be a meta description between 50 and 160 characters.
+      If unsure, keep it shorter than 160 characters.
      If the description is too long, shorten it. -->
  <style>
    [STANDARD_CSS_HERE]
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="slide-counter">
    <span id="slideNumber">1</span> / <span id="totalSlides">0</span>
  </div>

  <div class="presentation-container">
    <!-- First slide MUST have class "slide active" -->
    <div class="slide active">
      <h1>Title Here</h1>
      <p>Subtitle here</p>
    </div>

    <!-- All other slides MUST have class "slide" only -->
    <div class="slide">
      <h2>Slide Title</h2>
      <p>Content here</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="navigation">
    <button class="nav-btn" id="prevBtn" onclick="changeSlide(-1)" disabled>\u2190 Previous</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" id="nextBtn" onclick="changeSlide(1)">Next \u2192</button>
  </div>

  <script>
    [STANDARD_JAVASCRIPT_HERE]
  </script>
</body>
</html>

CRITICAL SLIDE REQUIREMENTS:
- Each slide MUST use: min-height: 100vh; display: none; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; padding: 60px 0;
- First slide MUST have class "slide active" with display: flex
- All other slides MUST have class "slide" with display: none
- Use professional gradient background: background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);

CRITICAL JAVASCRIPT REQUIREMENTS:
- NEVER declare DOM query variables (document.querySelectorAll, document.getElementById, etc.) at the global/module level
- ALL DOM queries MUST be declared INSIDE the functions that use them
- This ensures fresh DOM references are obtained each time a function is called
- Example: const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide"); MUST be inside showSlide() and changeSlide(), NOT outside

STANDARD CSS TEMPLATE (Use this exact CSS):
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
  color: #ffffff;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.presentation-container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 20px;
  position: relative;
}

.slide {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 60px 0;
  animation: slideIn 0.6s ease-out;
}

.slide.active {
  display: flex;
}

@keyframes slideIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

h1 {
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #a8a8a8 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  color: #ffffff;
}

h3 {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #e0e0e0;
}

p {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: #b8b8b8;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 20px;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.slide-counter {
  position: fixed;
  top: 20px;
  right: 30px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  z-index: 1000;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.navigation {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 30px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-btn {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.nav-btn:disabled {
  opacity: 0.3;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

.highlight-box {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 30px;
  margin: 30px auto;
  max-width: 700px;
}

.indicators-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
  margin: 40px 0;
  max-width: 900px;
}

.indicator-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 25px;
  text-align: left;
}

.checkmark {
  color: #4ade80;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin-right: 8px;
}

.metrics-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 25px;
  margin: 40px 0;
  max-width: 900px;
}

.metric-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 30px;
}

.metric-number {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: #4ade80;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.metric-label {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #b8b8b8;
}

.benchmark-table {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 30px auto;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.benchmark-table th,
.benchmark-table td {
  padding: 15px 20px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.benchmark-table th {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #ffffff;
}

.risk-list,
.success-list {
  list-style: none;
  text-align: left;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 30px auto;
}

.risk-list li,
.success-list li {
  padding: 15px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.risk-list li {
  background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
  border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
}

.success-list li {
  background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
  border-left: 4px solid #4ade80;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
  h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  p { font-size: 1rem; }

  .slide { padding: 40px 0; }
  .navigation { bottom: 20px; }
  .nav-btn { padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .indicators-grid,
  .metrics-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .slide-counter { font-size: 0.9rem; top: 15px; right: 15px; }
}

STANDARD JAVASCRIPT TEMPLATE (Use this exact JavaScript):
let currentSlide = 0;

function showSlide(n) {
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  const totalSlides = slides.length;
  
  document.getElementById("totalSlides").textContent = totalSlides;
  
  slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
  currentSlide = (n + totalSlides) % totalSlides;
  slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
  document.getElementById("slideNumber").textContent = currentSlide + 1;
  document.getElementById("prevBtn").disabled = currentSlide === 0;
  document.getElementById("nextBtn").disabled = currentSlide === totalSlides - 1;
}

function changeSlide(direction) {
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  const totalSlides = slides.length;
  
  if (direction === 1 && currentSlide < totalSlides - 1) {
    showSlide(currentSlide + 1);
  } else if (direction === -1 && currentSlide > 0) {
    showSlide(currentSlide - 1);
  }
}

document.addEventListener("keydown", function (e) {
  if (e.key === "ArrowRight" || e.key === " ") {
    e.preventDefault();
    changeSlide(1);
  } else if (e.key === "ArrowLeft") {
    e.preventDefault();
    changeSlide(-1);
  }
});

showSlide(0);

AVAILABLE COMPONENTS (Use these exact HTML patterns):

1. HIGHLIGHT BOX:
<div class="highlight-box">
  <h3>Title Here</h3>
  <p>Content here</p>
</div>

2. INDICATOR GRID:
<div class="indicators-grid">
  <div class="indicator-card">
    <h4><span class="checkmark">\u2713</span> Card Title</h4>
    <p>Card content here</p>
  </div>
</div>

3. METRICS GRID:
<div class="metrics-grid">
  <div class="metric-card">
    <span class="metric-number">85%</span>
    <div class="metric-label">Success rate</div>
  </div>
</div>

4. DATA TABLE:
<table class="benchmark-table">
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Header 1</th><th>Header 2</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Data 1</td><td>Data 2</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

5. RISK LIST:
<div class="risk-list">
  <li>Risk item here</li>
</div>

6. SUCCESS LIST:
<div class="success-list">
  <li>Success item here</li>
</div>

MOBILE RESPONSIVE: Include standard mobile breakpoints at 768px and 480px.

Always generate complete, self-contained HTML with all CSS and JavaScript inline. Focus on professional business presentations with clean, modern design.`,yW=s3.object({requestAnalysis:s3.string().describe("Brief analysis of presentation request. What topic? Target audience? Number of slides needed?"),presentationType:s3.enum(["business","sales","technical","educational","product","strategy"]).describe("Type of presentation. Choose: business, sales, technical, educational, product, or strategy"),slideCount:s3.number().min(3).max(20).describe("Recommended number of slides based on content. Minimum 3, maximum 20 for optimal engagement"),keyComponents:s3.array(s3.string()).describe("Key components needed (e.g., 'metrics', 'tables', 'highlight-boxes', 'indicators', 'risk-list')"),designStyle:s3.enum(["professional","modern","minimal","bold","corporate"]).describe("Visual design style to match brand. Options: professional, modern, minimal, bold, corporate")});(0,tC.tool)({description:"Analyze presentation request and create implementation plan with slideshow templates",inputSchema:yW,execute:async(e,t)=>{l(t,{message:`Planning a ${e.slideCount}-slide ${e.presentationType} presentation \u{1F9E0}\u26A1`});let r=yJ;return r+=`


